The paper proposes a new method for clustering data sets, which is a common problem in machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also deals with data analysis and statistics, which are related to cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). Finally, the paper uses experiments with image data, which is related to cs.CV (Computer Vision).
